description:
Takeo Goda is a GIANT guy with a GIANT heart.

Too bad the girls don’t want him! (They want his good-looking best friend, Sunakawa.)

Used to being on the sidelines, Takeo simply stands tall and accepts his fate. But one day when he saves a girl named Yamato from a harasser on the train, his (love!) life suddenly takes an incredible turn!

Takeo can hardly believe it when he crosses paths with Yamato again, and he finds himself falling in love with her… But with handsome Sunakawa around, does Takeo even stand a chance?

The origin of Marvel's premiere kid super-team establishes a new continuity for the Pack!

description: The first battle between the Zulus and the British find that the British are woefully unprepared. In the battle of Isandhlwana, the Zulus destroy the main army and massacre and mutilate the fallen British. Considered one of the worst defeats in English history, the battle was labeled by some as the beginning of the end of the British Empire as a global superpower.

Veronica's falling in love - with windsurfing! Jealous Archie is determined to learn the sport as well, but given that he might possibly be the clumsiest person that ever walked the face of the planet, things don't go very well. Desperate to learn, he takes lessons from the only expert in town: Cheryl Blossom! With a 'Little Archie' variant cover by Art Baltazar & Franco of Tiny Titans fame, this book will fly off the shelves!

description:
Grab your surfboard and hang ten with Archie and the gang! Well, at very least watch Archie try to hang ten! But he's not the only Riverdale teen who's having some tough luck on sand and in surf! See what happens in 'The Usual Crowd,' the hilarious lead story to another great fun-filled double digest.

description:
The Scarsbury Slobberknocker!

A new challenger takes the stage! He's hungry for wins...and it's feeding time! Plus: witness the tragic event that drove Bunyan into a life of bear-graps!
name: The Scarsbury Slobberknocker!

description:
It's a brand new day in Freak Out City, the raptors have gone to ground and Blastosaurus is about to begin his first day as an official officer of the law (along with Naomi Fenton as his reluctant partner). It's hard to juggle real detective work with the demands of his incomprehensible superior Captain Haverstock Corinthian Gribblehurst Harris.

Meanwhile, the kids are off to investigate an apparently haunted house but when they arrive things are far more sinister and unsettling than they could have imagined.

The Clawed-Agent Strikes!

Jumping to the year 2016, the Clawed-Agent is forced out of retirement when the nefarious Boom Operator starts leveling buildings in New York City. Now with the She-Agent by his side, the duo must work together to take down this psychotic terrorist, while they discover a more sinister plot behind it all.
name: The Clawed-Agent Strikes!

description:
The Death Cult of Mississippi

The highly anticipated third installment of The Brothers James brings Jack and John to Mississippi, but they didn't get there alone...and they may not make it out alive. In The Death Cult of Mississippi, the brothers must survive a maniacal death cult and a mysterious new presence in their life; one who's involvement may reach far, far deeper than the brothers could imagine.

Meet Avion Davis a world famous super model who’s been transformed by a Catalyst meteor into the horrific shambling monster called Terrain. He’s obsessed over reversing the effects and he’s willing to take out anyone that gets in his way and that includes QUINCREDIBLE!
Gavin and Doug journey to London to become the newest members of the Brigade, but will their first mission be their last?

Chapter Two

Jim and his partner, Crunchy, get caught up in a deadly high-speed chase - a taste of the challenges to come. Back in the present day, Eve and Max get rough with Jake and his boys. She can't shake the thought: does Max know the truth about Jim's fate?
name: Chapter Two

description: The story darkens as the enemy is revealed. The Judge and Minnesota's search for answers leads them to a mysterious place that hides a dark secret. Meanwhile, back in Redemption, the residents struggle with the aftermath from the previous day and set out for answers of their own. Little do they know the fate of the town sets with the sun.
